.\" Manpage for HSH
.TH man 1 "24 October 2021" "1.0" "hsh man page"
.SH PROLOG
This manual page is for ALX-Holberton project called simple_shell where we create our own shell that interprets command.
.SH NAME
hsh - holberton shell, simple command language interpreter
.SH SYNOPSIS
hsh [command_file [argument ...]]
.SH DESCRIPTION
The hsh utility is a command language interpreter that shall execute commands read from a command line string, the standard input, or a specified file.
.SH OPERANDS
The following operands are supported:
.RS 3
command_file - The pathname of a file containing commands.
.RS 0
argument - The arguments/parameters for the command_file
.SH SEE ALSO
.I sh(1)
.SH AUTHOR
.RS 3
ELIYAS FISEHA asbezah@gmail.com
